      "value": "<p><strong>Level 2</strong> Enchantment</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 60 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 1 minute</p>\n\nYou weave a distracting string of words, causing creatures of your choice that you can see within range to make a Wisdom saving throw. Any creature you or your companions are fighting automatically succeeds on this save. On a failed save, a target has a -10 penalty to Wisdom (Perception|XPHB) checks and Passive Perception|XPHB until the spell ends.",
